ms.safi.btsync.dto

Class File

  • Object
    • ms.safi.btsync.dto.File

  • public class File
extends Object
    JavaBean implementation of a file's information from BitTorrent Sync.

    An example of a file's information: 

     {
      "have_pieces": 1,
      "name": "index.html",
      "size": 2726,
      "state": "created",
      "total_pieces": 1,
      "type": "file",
      "download": 1 // only for selective sync folders
 }
    Author:
    Omeed Safi
